TEXT -1736 -672 Left 2 ;*Note that it is not possible to accurately model relays or mechanical switches in Spice,\nbut we need them on the PCB.\n \nAlso, the logic gates and transistors are behavioral models and not the same as the \nselected components.Spicelines within these components are modified to reflect \nintended behavior as close as possible such as supply voltages for gates. \nModels for these components are not available publicly.
