TEXT -1728 872 Left 2 ;FAULT CURRENT\nREF\n(for CT)
TEXT -1736 -416 Left 2 ;Not simulated also are the opto-isolators which are needed to step-down\n24V inputs from BMS and IMD fault into 5V
