TEXT 2936 -936 Left 2 ;In reality, what I want to do is use 4x NMOS to pull down the minus(-) terminal\nof the coil, and use the latch signal as an input to each gate. \nModeling relays in spice is something I haven't figured out how to do yet\n \nThe reason for 4x NMOS pull-downs is that there are 3 latch signals that control it,\nplus the start-up signal (which actually should be a PMOS).
